    "description": {
      "description": "<p>Arremesso, Receita</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Granada que cria um pulso cinético violento, empurrando todos para longe do seu ponto de impacto.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Uso:</span> Arremesso.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Tempo de preparo:</span> 1 ação.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Alcance:</span> 7/21m.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Dano:</span> [1].</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Efeitos:</span> Impacto (4). Empurra tudo para 2+COG<span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">/2</span> metros de distância do local do pulso. <span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\"> </span>Os atingidos fazem teste de FIS (dif16) para diminuir o empurrão pela metade +MS metros.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Preço:</span> 2 pratas.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Ofício:</span> Engenharia N5.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Tempo para fabricar:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> 12 horas.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Materiais:</span> 3 de Metal<span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:8.0pt;line-height:105%;mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:bl